(10, 1, '2019-02-05 23:55:40', '2019-02-05 23:55:40', '<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[81],\"align\":\"left\",\"className\":\"alignleft\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery alignleft columns-1 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/ana/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/baked-goods-bread-food-209194-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"81\" data-link=\"http://localhost/ana/wordpress2/productos/baked-goods-bread-food-209194/\" class=\"wp-image-81\"/></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Pan multigrano</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pepitas, amaranto y nuez, la mezlca perfecta.<br>Precio: $5.00 </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":84,\"width\":305,\"height\":203} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/ana/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bake-baked-blur-209215-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-84\" width=\"305\" height=\"203\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Baguette</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:left\">\n\nPepitas, amaranto y nuez, la mezlca perfecta.<br>Precio: $5.00\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Productos', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'productos', '', '', '2019-02-07 22:53:01', '2019-02-07 22:53:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ana/wordpress2/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2019-02-05 23:55:40', '2019-02-05 23:55:40', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nIt is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using \'Content here, content here\', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for \'lorem ipsum\' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":67} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://localhost/ana/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/baked-goods-bread-cake-873653-1024x757.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-67\"/><figcaption>Nuestra historia, como todo en la vida, empezó en casa.</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Historia', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'historia', '', '', '2019-02-06 00:41:17', '2019-02-06 00:41:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ana/wordpress2/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(12, 1, '2019-02-05 23:55:40', '2019-02-05 23:55:40', '<!-- wp:pirate-forms/form {\"html\":\"\\n\\n\\u003cdiv class=\\u0022pirate_forms_container widget-no\\u0022 id=\\u0022pirate_forms_container_default\\u0022\\u003e\\n\\t\\u003c!\\u002d\\u002d header \\u002d\\u002d\\u003e\\n\\t\\n\\t\\u003c!\\u002d\\u002d thank you \\u002d\\u002d\\u003e\\n\\t\\n\\t\\u003cdiv class=\\u0022pirate_forms_wrap\\u0022\\u003e\\n\\t\\u003c!\\u002d\\u002d errors \\u002d\\u002d\\u003e\\n\\t\\n\\t\\u003c!\\u002d\\u002d form \\u002d\\u002d\\u003e\\n\\n\\t\\t\\u003cform\\n\\t\\t\\tmethod=\\u0022post\\u0022\\n\\t\\t\\tenctype=\\u0022application/x-www-form-urlencoded\\u0022\\n\\t\\t\\tclass=\\u0022pirate_forms  form_honeypot-on wordpress-nonce-on pirate-forms-contact-name-on pirate-forms-contact-email-on pirate-forms-contact-subject-on pirate-forms-contact-message-on pirate-forms-contact-submit-on pirate-forms-contact-referrer-on pirate_forms_from_form-on\\u0022\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u003e\\n\\t\\t\\t\\u003cdiv class=\\u0022pirate_forms_three_inputs_wrap \\u0022\\u003e\\n\\t\\n\\n\\u003cdiv class=\\u0022col-xs-12 pirate_forms_three_inputs form_field_wrap contact_name_wrap col-xs-12 col-sm-6 contact_name_wrap pirate_forms_three_inputs form_field_wrap\\u0022\\u003e\\n\\t\\t\\u003cinput type=\\u0022text\\u0022 class=\\u0022form-control\\u0022 id=\\u0022pirate-forms-contact-name\\u0022 name=\\u0022pirate-forms-contact-name\\u0022 class=\\u0022\\u0022 placeholder=\\u0022Nombre\\u0022 required oninvalid=\\u0022this.setCustomValidity(\'Enter your name\')\\u0022 onchange=\\u0022this.setCustomValidity(\'\')\\u0022 value=\\u0022\\u0022 \\u003e\\n\\u003c/div\\u003e\\n\\n\\n\\u003cdiv class=\\u0022col-xs-12 pirate_forms_three_inputs form_field_wrap contact_email_wrap col-xs-12 col-sm-6 contact_email_wrap pirate_forms_three_inputs form_field_wrap\\u0022\\u003e\\n\\t\\t\\u003cinput type=\\u0022email\\u0022 class=\\u0022form-control\\u0022 id=\\u0022pirate-forms-contact-email\\u0022 name=\\u0022pirate-forms-conta